                "<strong>Diffie-Hellman Key Exchange</strong>: undefined",
                "<strong>Double Ratchet Algorithm</strong>: undefined"
              ]
            },
            "note": {
              "text": "WhatsApp is a masterclass in managing persistent state and high-frequency events."
