            "box": {
              "title": "Technical Details",
              "list": [
                "<strong>mechanism</strong>: Distributed transaction or Atomic lock in Redis",
                "<strong>process</strong>: 1. Find best driver. 2. Attempt to 'Lock' driver in Redis for 30s. 3. If success, notify driver. 4. If driver accepts, finalize match. 5. If driver rejects, release lock and find next best."
